page_0:    "I've grabbed as much loot as I could carry, but there is still some left. I'm leaving this note for myself in case I dare to come back. I found a few of the laborer's tunnels to help ease my looting. Funny thing that, the workers tend to be the biggest thieves.
There's evidence that the Hammers were here recently, and I'm sure that they stashed something, but why here? Probably in the Mausoleum itself, but I fear it is far too dangerous to negotiate alone. No loss - my next venture will be the Mystic Soul and I hear that it's worth is extraordinary.

Adolpho"